Sentencas: The influence of reduction and re-oxidation cycles on microstructure and residual stress of anode supported planar solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) has been studied.
Titulo: Reduction and re-oxidation of anodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Shrinkage caused by the reduction of NiO to Ni is not reversible.
Titulo: Reduction and re-oxidation of anodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Microstructural scanning electron microscope observations reveal that after re-oxidation, the NiO has a higher porosity and requires a larger volume than in the initial, oxidised state.
Titulo: Reduction and re-oxidation of anodes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: As a consequence of the anode expansion, tensile stresses develop in the electrolyte, ultimately causing fracture.
Titulo: Reduction and re-oxidation of anodes for solid oxide fuel cells
